I started this adventure as a Gardner. 
He called me once and he was like “Nice to meet you Michele, I’m the director of a movie called 365 Days, I don’t know you.. but I need you”.
I couldn't know what was going to happen next, but I was crazy enough to leave my “normal” life to dream with him.
Thank you @tomasz_mandes.official for your friendship, your brotherhood, your respect, your advices.. but especially, thank you for that phone call.. the phone call that changed my life.
I’M HAPPY.
#365daysforever
